Here are the steps:

1- Open your explorer and find "Steam Games"
2- Open "Steamapps"
3- Open "common"
4- Find "SCP Secret Laboratory" and open it
5- Open "Translations"
6- Remove "English (Default)"
7- Copy the modified "English (Default)" file you just dowloaded and paste it in.

You can now open and run your game. Enjoy watching the sillyness!
